    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In Buddhism and Hinduism, incantations of sacred Sanskrit or pseudo-Sanskrit syllables or phrases that are used as protective devices and to support concentration; they reference short summaries of the essential doctrine contained in a much longer sacred text.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
